<div style="background: var(--cream);">
  <div class="reviews-section" id="reviews">
    <div class="reviews-hero-img reveal">
      <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AppaaThe/Rituel-store/main/product-images/rituel-guasha-closeup-inuse.png" alt="Close-up of amethyst gua sha stone being used on face" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <div class="reviews-header">
      <span class="section-label reveal">The Ritual</span>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">Real results.<br><em>Real commitment.</em></h2>
      <p class="reviews-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">5 minutes every morning. That's the only secret.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reviews-promise reveal">
      <div class="promise-grid">
        <div class="promise-item">
          <span class="promise-num">01</span>
          <h3>Visible from day one</h3>
          <p>Gua sha physically moves fluid and boosts circulation. You'll see less puffiness after your very first session.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="promise-item">
          <span class="promise-num">02</span>
          <h3>Better with consistency</h3>
          <p>Like any ritual, the results compound. By week 2-3, the difference becomes something other people notice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="promise-item">
          <span class="promise-num">03</span>
          <h3>Backed by your guarantee</h3>
          <p>Try it for 30 days. If you don't see results, we'll refund every penny. No questions, no hassle.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
.reviews-promise {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.promise-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 40px;
}
.promise-item {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px 24px;
}
.promise-num {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--terracotta);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  opacity: 0.6;
}
.promise-item h3 {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--espresso);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.promise-item p {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--stone);
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .promise-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .promise-item {
    padding: 24px 16px;
  }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Testimonials",
  "presets": [{ "name": "Testimonials" }]
}
{% endschema %}
